{"tid":864695,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈過龍？】水藍．天岸特色戶1500萬沽　低估價三成","createTime":"2018-10-16T11:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T14:16:03.000Z","uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5363f2f67a53d1f335c2ed1346ef2b42dae73d1e","tid":864695,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181016/photo/bkn-20181016171202197-1016_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181016173206\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181016%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181016171202197-1016_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181016173206&h=e8752176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東涌大跌價，罕有特色戶都要劈價出貨。東涌物業曾偉明表示，水藍．天岸連天台單位，實用面積1,041方呎，內置樓梯直達面積694方呎天台，設按摩池，同區放盤及成交都不多，有銀行估價達約2,100萬。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，上址原業主曾於區內持有數個物業，早年已移居外地，近年已積極沽貨，曾叫價1,800萬元放售上述單位，但近月市靜，雖然叫價已低於估價，但仍被準買家壓價，終以1,500萬元出貨，新買家為外區客，呎價約14,409元。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，單位2008年一手購入已達1,181萬元，持貨10年帳面只賺319萬元，期內只升值約27%，升幅跑輸大市。"},{"pid":"0ff5a9cbb7f006f2a005698e17f937f4ee5b8620","tid":864695,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:37:15.000Z","msg":"10年都係升27%, 唔撚係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5375b0b57c9ba5b86b5bf1c3abae91b37c3d29","tid":864695,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5eec64f2759099d14eff023c4d186b2b94badb91","tid":864695,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"特色戶個價一向不能作準"},{"pid":"08dc2b1a10c93348ffdd0fb5938fabfcd9d300dc","tid":864695,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba10e96ddce3d3d0feac3759fd4aec9f08ad910","tid":864695,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b5375b0b57c9ba5b86b5bf1c3abae91b37c